extends layout.pug

block scripts
    link(href='stylesheets/logs.css', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    link(href='stylesheets/myaccount.css', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css')
    script(src='https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js')
    script(src='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js')

block content
    body
        .container
            .sidenav
                a(href='/myaccount') My Orders
                a(href='/logs') Dashboard (admin)
                a(href='/additems') Add Sale Item (admin)
                a(href='#') Submit a Design
                a(href='#') Sign Out
            .main
                h1(style='text-align: center;') Submit a Design
                hr
                // Trigger the modal with a button
                button.btn.btn-lg.pull-right(type='button', data-toggle='modal', data-target='#myModal' style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif") 
                    Upload Design
                br
                br
                // Modal
                #myModal.modal.fade(role='dialog')
                    .modal-dialog
                        // Modal content
                        .modal-content
                            .modal-header
                                button.close(type='button', data-dismiss='modal') ×
                                h4.modal-title Submit Your Own Design
                            .modal-body(style='font-size:13px')
                                form.form-horizontal(action='/action_page.php')
                                    .form-group
                                        label.control-label.col-sm-2(for='email') Name of your Design:
                                        .col-sm-10
                                            input#email.form-control(type='email', placeholder='Enter name', name='id')
                                    .form-group
                                        label.control-label.col-sm-2(for='pwd') Link to Bio:
                                        .col-sm-10
                                            input#pwd.form-control(type='password', placeholder='Enter link to bio (google doc)', name='name')
                                    .form-group
                                        label.control-label.col-sm-2(for='pwd') File:
                                        .col-sm-10
                                            input#pwd.form-control(type='password', placeholder='Upload file', name='desc')
                                    .form-group
                                        .col-sm-offset-2.col-sm-10
                                            button.btn.btn-default(type='submit') Submit
    p
        | We are a group of 4 Computer Science students developing an e-commerce website for our Senior Design Project. Our website is a platform for art and design students to showcase their talent and creativity, so we are looking for students to submit their designs! We are selling T-shirts with designs from UC Davis students to support the art community. For each shirt sold ($10), the designer/artist will get $1 (about 25% of the earnings after tshirt fees, paypal fees, etc.). We also promote the artist/designer on our page by sharing an About Me” of them and linking their portfolio. Please email your design (png file) following these specifications to 193tees@gmail.com.
        br
        br
        | Tell us where on the T-shirt you would like your design to be printed. Files should be set up to sizes not to exceed (to approximate size in inches divide pixels at each dimension by 300):
        br
        br
        | a) Full front or back, 14 x 16 @ 300dpi (4200 x 4800 pixels).
        br
        br
        | b) Left or right chest, 4 x 4 though 1 x 4 is recommended (300 x 1200)
        br
        br
        | The design can be anything of your choice that you think people will love or our current theme: Spring!
        br
        br
        | Email us if you have any questions!
